OL,3,CConsumer confidence 'bleak' as public
OL,4,Cbraces for Budget
OL,6,FConsumer confidence has fallen across
OL,7,Fall measures as the public braces for
OL,8,Fdifficult news in next week's Budget,
OL,9,Ffigures show.
OL,11,FGfK's long-running Consumer Confidence
OL,12,FIndex fell by two points to minus 19
OL,13,Fin November, with all five measures
OL,14,Ffrom confidence in the general economy
OL,15,Fto spending expectations tumbling.
OL,17,FNeil Bellamy, consumer insights
OL,18,Fdirector at GfK, said: "This is a
OL,19,Fbleak set of results as we head
OL,20,Ftowards next week's Budget.
