OL,6,F"A fall across all five measures
OL,7,Fsuggests the public is bracing for
OL,8,Fdifficult news, with little in the
OL,9,Fcurrent climate to lift expectations."
OL,11,FForward-looking measures for
OL,12,Fconfidence in both personal finances
OL,13,Fand the general economy both fell by
OL,14,Ftwo points ` although the personal
OL,15,Ffinances measure is an improvement of
OL,16,Ftwo points compared to this time last
OL,17,Fyear.
