OL,6,FHowever, at minus 32, expectations for
OL,7,Fthe general economic situation over
OL,8,Fthe next 12 months is now six points
OL,9,Fworse than last November.
OL,11,FGfk said a three-point drop in the
OL,12,Fmajor purchase index ` an indicator of
OL,13,Fconfidence in buying big ticket items
OL,14,F` to minus 15 is also "troubling at
OL,15,Fthis time of year, suggesting
OL,16,Fhouseholds are tightening their grip
OL,17,Fjust as retailers move into a crucial
OL,18,Ftrading period".
